item.title: Times Are Tough, Cell Phones Are Free
item.description:
With the current economic climate, most people are looking for ways to save money. Instead of spending lavishly, it’s wiser to be cautious and prepare for potential tough times ahead. One way to save money is by finding deals on essential items like cell phone services and devices. Many people purchase their cell phones from carrier stores or large retailers, but these places often charge a premium for the phones themselves...
